
Ranger Help for: swamp
======================

SUMMARY:    
The swamp is a dark looking place, wet and dank. There are many trees and
stumps, with standing water everywhere. Life is abundant here, as well as
the Ranger population. Most Ranger skills will work in the swamp terrain.
Swamps can be found on Darkwind, and Kerei.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

